# deforum-next-core

Python core engine for Deforum Next MVP:
- schema (Pydantic)
- timeline curves (linear / bezier / catmull-rom)
- camera rig (LookAt quaternion)
- FastAPI bridge
- CLI

See root `README.md` for quickstart.
